Choose a Client to Reveal a Story






American Express
											




 Producer of multiple key communication projects including:
The introduction of Six Sigma into a service organization. Support of Membership Revitalization initiative. Internal launch of the Optima Card. Creation of Leadership Summit Innovation materials. The production of quarterly employee communication such as Customer Focused Sales, Tiger Woods and the Brand, and numerous other projects.







												Beehive Media
											




 MMG working with Beehive Media created promotional videos for Sorouh Real Estates Dubai Sales Office. The videos were incorporated into an interactive immersive environment for consumers visiting the development office.
                                        
MMG later assisted Beehive Media in the development of a demonstration video for their three tiered project visualization tool K-Space for developers and property management companies.
 






												Boy Scouts - Denver Council
											




 Committed to getting the word out, MMG partnered with the Denver Area Council of the Boy Scouts of America on multiple projects. A multi-year relationship, MMG provided strategy, tactics and content to the council.
                                       
                                       Notable projects included a 30 minute PBS special "The Truths of Scouting", a celebration of 100 Years of Scouting and yearly "Sports Breakfast'fundraising videos. MMG is proud to support this great organization and all it does for the Denver community. 






												Colorado Enterprise Fund
											




 Colorado Enterprise Fund, called upon MMG to assist them in celebrating 30 years of community based lending.
                                        
                                        The stories of entrepeneurial innovation surround interviews MMG conducted with board members, financial leaders and Colorado Governor, John Hickelooper. The video was initially used at a celebration dinner but also serves as a tool for presentations and on the web. 






												Diacor
											




 MMG provided high level demonstration and explanations for Diacor's revolutionary "Air Bearing" patient transfer system.
                                        
                                        Utilizing an interview with a leading cancer care practioner, MMG combined both macro imagery of the device with treatment demonstration footage to convey the anvantages and use of the "Air Bearing" system. The multiple segments produced are used inside of presentations, tradeshows and across the web. 






												Excel Foundation - Tamarisk Coalition
											




Excel Energy Foundation worked with MMG to tell the story of the Tamarisk Coalition's western river restoration efforts. Shot in a single day on location, the video needed to communicate the mission Xcel Energy has in supporting the communities they serve, while clearly conveying the importance of the work that the Tamarisk Coalition is engaged in.






												John Ward Golf
											




 Working with john Ward - Golf Instructor, PGA Professional - MMG scripted, planned and produced the Missing Link instructional putting system. Shot on location in Denver Colorado, the shows were produced on budget and inside of a single day of shooting. 






												Long Drivers of America
											




 Working with Long Drivers of America, MMG developed show flow, creative approaches, roll-in video, live show call and on site video production for the broadcast of the Worl Long Drive Championship.
                                        










												McGhee Productivity Solutions
											




 Working with McGhee Productivity Solutions, MMG developed a sales video for their latest e-mail productivity training course.
                                        
                                        Tied to their industry leading "Take Back Your Life" course, the e-mail video operated as a lead generator and low bar of entry way to rest of McGhee's business and personal productivity solutions.  






			Miller Coors
											




 MMG worked with Coors communications deprtment and senior management to develop content for multiple high visibility projects. 
                                        Over the years MMG delivered multiple consumer messaging strategies for senior leadership presentations and designed, coordinated and produced  convention mateerials including; presentation templates and signage. MMG also concieved, produced and staged brand education sessions at the Coors annual distributor conventions. 

MMG also played a key role in lifting Coors in-field display execution by distributor staff to another level with the Quarterly print and video communication â€“ "Gaining The Retail Edge".
 






												Mirada Medical
											




 MMG worked with Mirada Medical to create a dynamic and informative animated video that explained the benefits of their visualization and productivity tool for tumor board patient reviews.
                                        
                                        Created to be part of a new Mirada Medical sales communication plan, the CaseMeeting video was deployed on the Mirada Medical website and used in face-to-face, email, and social media communications. 






												RE/MAX LLC.
											




 MMG works with RE/MAX's senior management to develop content for multiple high-level projects. Scripting of convention themes and leadership presentations, strategy and content development on Government, Banking, Fannie Mae, HUD, HAFA and Housing Summit programs and presentations. We also work as a producer of Broker and Agent training programs, charitable projects and brand communications.

Recently MMG was the content architect and SME for the development and launch the "Mometum" complete broker training program.


 






												Rockefeller Brother's Fund
											




 MMG working with The Rockefeller Brothers Fund created program videos for both internal communication and public facing program awareness efforts.
                                        When RBF moved to their new offices at 475 Riverside Drive, they called on MMG to produce videos that highlighted their sustainable building practices and the LEED platinum certification they recieved. 






												United Way of New York City
											




 MMG Worked with United Way of New York City Communication Team to develop content to fit their communication strategies for annual fundraising efforts. 
                                        
                                        True documentary filmmaking, MMG was called upon to gain people's trust quickly as we walked into their homes and lives. These powerful stories then contributed to year to year increases in giving to UWNYC. 






												Qwest
											




 MMG created the post US West/Qwest merger presentation and content for the introduction of the company to Wall Street.
                                        Working on a tight time frame with very few "new resources" and inside of a newly merged culture, MMG was able to communicate the companies expanded capabilities to Wall Street investors and analysts.  






												US West
											




 MMG partnered with US West for numerous projects over many years. Noteworthy were the introduction of their Olympic Sponsorship and the development of the investor road show video wall to support senior management messaging prior to the merger with Qwest. 









